append-rfoc: {DΔ: pos -> pos}
  rfoc (DΔ ·)
  -> rfoc _Δ 
  -> rfoc (DΔ _Δ) 
  -> type.
%mode append-rfoc +DΔ +V₁ +V₂ -V.

-: append-rfoc ([δ] δ) ·R V₂ V₂. % Actual base case
-: append-rfoc ([δ] ·) _ _ ·R. % Would be suprious if we had linearity
-: append-rfoc ([δ] c Q⁺ , DΔ δ) (cR X V₁) V₂ (cR X V)
  <- append-rfoc ([δ] DΔ δ) V₁ V₂ (V: rfoc (DΔ _Δ)).
-: append-rfoc ([δ] ↓ A⁻ , DΔ δ) (↓R N V₁) V₂ (↓R N V)
  <- append-rfoc ([δ] DΔ δ) V₁ V₂ (V: rfoc (DΔ _Δ)).
-: append-rfoc ([δ] A⁺ ⊕ B⁺ , DΔ δ) (⊕R₁ V₁) V₂ (⊕R₁ V)
  <- append-rfoc ([δ] A⁺ , DΔ δ) V₁ V₂ (V: rfoc (A⁺ , DΔ _Δ)).
-: append-rfoc ([δ] A⁺ ⊕ B⁺ , DΔ δ) (⊕R₂ V₁) V₂ (⊕R₂ V)
  <- append-rfoc ([δ] B⁺ , DΔ δ) V₁ V₂ (V: rfoc (B⁺ , DΔ _Δ)).
-: append-rfoc ([δ] 1 , DΔ δ) (1R V₁) V₂ (1R V)
  <- append-rfoc ([δ] DΔ δ) V₁ V₂ (V: rfoc (DΔ _Δ)).
-: append-rfoc ([δ] A⁺ ⊗ B⁺ , DΔ δ) (⊗R V₁) V₂ (⊗R V)
  <- append-rfoc ([δ] A⁺ , B⁺ , DΔ δ) V₁ V₂ V.

%worlds (atom⁻ | atom⁺ | x⁻ | x⁺) (append-rfoc _ _ _ _).
%total V (append-rfoc _ V _ _).

